import { createApp } from 'vue'
import App from './App.vue'
import GAuth from 'vue3-google-oauth2'
import store from './store'

const app = createApp(App)
const gAuthOptions = { clientId: '613890288014-t1s0dqvpmtr4mgraknf606hegm48oump.apps.googleusercontent.com', scope: 'email', prompt: 'consent', fetch_basic_profile: false }

app.mount('#app')
app.use(store)
app.use(GAuth, gAuthOptions)

/*
 * 전역 변수
*/
app.config.globalProperties.$store = store
app.config.globalProperties.axiosConfig = { headers : { "Content-Type" : "application/json" } }
